<FlowDocument PagePadding="5,0,5,0" AllowDrop="True" NumberSubstitution.CultureSource="User" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Verdana" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">Watermark Image Opacity</Run></Paragraph><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">If you like to have semi-transparent watermark image to add to your main image, you can specify the opacity (alpha) value here. 1 means no opacity, while 0 mean total transparent. If you set the opacity value to 0, the program will ignore the action to add watermark image.</Run></Paragraph></FlowDocument>